## Case 1: Simple Value Patch
+ /users/admin/role: "super-user";

## Case 2: Attaching Schema to a Path
+ /users/{ $id }: ( !^$email, ?^&active );

## Case 3: Complex Patch with Snatch and Catch
+ /users/{ $id }: [ //last_login! ] {
    !!($id, "Logged in!")
};

## Case 4: Custom Type Patching
+ /transactions/{ $id }: [ @USD amount, @Date timestamp ] {
    amount |> __("validate") |> !
};
